{"content": "I need to multiply 475\u2089 \u00d7 582\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n475\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 5\u00d79\u2070 = 4\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 5\u00d71 = 324 + 63 + 5 = 392\u2081\u2080\n\n582\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 405 + 72 + 2 = 479\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n392 \u00d7 479 = 187,768\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n187768 \u00f7 9 = 20863 r 1\n20863 \u00f7 9 = 2318 r 1\n2318 \u00f7 9 = 257 r 5\n257 \u00f7 9 = 28 r 5\n28 \u00f7 9 = 3 r 1\n3 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 3\n\nReading from bottom to top: **315511\u2089**\n\n315511", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 325}